_sText:
Fedra is a nice little village set in the mountains. The counterterroists' spawn is around and in a small house that is near bombspot A and a stretch away from B. The terrorists spawn point is on the other end of the village, equidistant to A and B. This is an extended version with changes such as: -models from the game S.T.A.L.K.E.R. -custom textures -A tunnelsystem -new ways to A and B -An elevator at bombspot A -more houses you can enter. There are: - 64 Player-spawns - 2 Bombspots - radar map in bsp - soundscapes - 3d skybox with moving clouds - use of hint/ skip texture and areaportals render-time: 1 min 58 sec Optimized, balanced and tested with and for 64 Players on the Sachsenkneipe servers. Special thanks to www.sachsenkneipe.de for testing and improving it! Sachsenkneipe XL - 64 Slots: 193.192.58.170:27015 Credits: -textures by valve and TopHATTwaffle (Textures For the Realworld pack) -Models by valve, GSC Game World (S.T.A.L.K.E.R.) and www.gaming-models.de. -skybox by [-B-] - converting for CSS, Original Authors -> Hipshot - making the origional Enjoy playing it :) wostok
